{"tid":2261537,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"碧咸咀對咀親吻愛女再惹熱議　英名嘴嫌古怪作家力撐","createTime":"2020-10-28T11:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T14:36:04.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1efa2dcf714155c6d93937cea7693a1f8af7003e","tid":2261537,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T11:39:52.000Z","msg":"「萬人迷」碧咸（David Beckham）愛女夏柏（Harper Seven Beckham）不經不覺已經9歲，樣子甚具少女味道。擺明車馬的偏心爸爸碧咸，社交媒體上時常上載跟女兒親暱合照，不過一張張咀對咀照片成為熱話，曾被英國名嘴Piers Morgan形容為毛骨悚然 （creepy）和古怪 （weird）。<br />\n<br />\n近日有寫作人為碧咸平反，認為只有變態的人才會將親吻女兒跟性愛扯上關係。<br />\n<br />\n女兒是爸爸的「前世情人」，在恨女恨到發燒的碧咸家，夏柏自出娘胎已受盡父母、三個兄長和家中長輩萬千寵愛，碧咸更是嚴重偏心到出面，他早前曾在美國名嘴Ellen DeGeneres的節目《The Ellen DeGeneres Show》中自爆，「我從不對女兒說不」。<br />\n<br />\n碧咸對三個兒子甚為嚴格，對他們的要求多數打回頭。相反，無論女兒想要什麼，他也無法拒絕，「其實我拒絕過她一次，然後她立即扁嘴&hellip;&hellip;」他停一停，露出一臉苦惱的樣子，「看過她那個樣子之後，我發誓不能再跟女兒說不。」"},{"pid":"82b35df555649c2a80ac4fc127b3325d956451ed","tid":2261537,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T11:40:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201028/398185494380285952146879.png/fhf1Zn6702B-4mF0xCqiBFsW_LHKJx7utZ4elbWeHpU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201028%2F398185494380285952146879.png%2Ffhf1Zn6702B-4mF0xCqiBFsW_LHKJx7utZ4elbWeHpU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=08424174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201028/398165735559794688250973.jpeg/103qTT1Nib9OWpFOUt1noAB7Nt_YPqQ6Nna7fDZ2u3w?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201028%2F398165735559794688250973.jpeg%2F103qTT1Nib9OWpFOUt1noAB7Nt_YPqQ6Nna7fDZ2u3w%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=4d7f5335&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201028/398165737757741056325107.png/pyByoH3CzYjx3taclHzdm4iQD5ElGaKLIM7cbCDO3Gw?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc